where/0000018c-3f84-dede-a7dd-3fc582b40000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡总理的联盟陷入了一个循环：立法者表达了他们的反对意见，但随后投票支持总理 ■ 在甘茨离开联盟之前，没有人会越界，但只要人质仍被扣押在以色列，他就不会这样做。加沙</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Dec 2023 17:59:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-06/ty-article/.premium/stuck-between-hamas-and-hezbollah-netanyahus-failed-government-isnt-going-anywhere/0000018c-3f84-dede-a7dd-3fc582b40000</guid></item><item><title>没有设备、人员或电力：加沙地带南部的医院因伤病人数过多而不堪重负</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-06/ty-article/.premium/hospitals-in-southern-gaza-strip-overwhelmed-by-scale-of-wounded-and-ill/0000018c-3e33-d11b-a3bf-febb23d70000</link><description>汗尤尼斯和拉法医院的医生告诉《国土报》，当地情况不断恶化，床位和物资匮乏，并且有可能爆发疾病，导致死亡人数飙升。如果疏散迫在眉睫，医生会问：“我们要去哪里？”我们可以将病人疏散到哪里？</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Dec 2023 15:49:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-06/ty-article/.premium/hospitals-in-southern-gaza-strip-overwhelmed-by-scale-of-wounded-and-ill/0000018c-3e33-d11b-a3bf-febb23d70000</guid></item><item><title>以色列对加沙地带的空袭将巴勒斯坦人推至埃及边境</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-06/ty-article/.premium/israeli-airstrikes-in-gaza-strip-push-palestinians-to-egyptian-border/0000018c-3f44-d826-ab9e-bfdfe3040000</link><description>来自加沙北部的数十万难民目前在南部避难 ■ 战争专家称，尽管拜登警告以色列要更加努力不要伤害平民，但以色列在加沙的行动似乎没有重大变化</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Dec 2023 14:45:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-06/ty-article/.premium/israeli-airstrikes-in-gaza-strip-push-palestinians-to-egyptian-border/0000018c-3f44-d826-ab9e-bfdfe3040000</guid></item><item><title>大屠杀并不能证明大屠杀是正当的：以色列、加沙和战争罪</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-12-06/ty-article-opinion/.premium/massacre-doesnt-justify-massacre-israel-gaza-and-war-crimes/0000018c-3585-d55e-adbf-7fd7c8900000</link><description>攻击我的《纽约时报》专栏文章的一群历史学家对以色列政策做出了令人尴尬的道歉，但没有谴责大量加沙平民死亡</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Dec 2023 14:16:04 GMT</pubDate><guid